const { isIE, isChrome, isOpera, isFirefox, isSafari } = _Brower;
{
    const s = Logger('测试浏览器类型判断');
    s.info(isIE);
    s.info(isChrome);
    s.info(isOpera);
    s.info(isFirefox);
    s.info(isSafari);
    s.info('---------------------');
    const test = [
        123,
        '123',
        true,
        { name: '张三' },
        function name() {
            return '张三';
        },
        /^\d+$/,
        null,
        undefined,
        [1, 2, 3],
        new Date(),
        new Error()
    ];
    test.forEach(item => {
        s.info(Type(item));
    });
}
